// eslint-disable-next-line
import React from 'react'
import Profile from './Profile'
import References from './References'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch} from 'react-router-dom'

function Body() {
    return (
            <Switch>
                <Route path="/">
                    <Profile />
                </Route>
                <Route path="/references">
                    <References/>
                </Route>
            </Switch>
    )
}

export default Body
